structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
PUBLIC WORKS IN CITIES OTHER THAN THE FIRST CLASS

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 234, sec. 11; and ch. 239, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1980; amended ch. 149, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2741L-1 to 2741L-19.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Alternate method for cities of second and sixth class to acquire and generate sewerage system -- Water system may be joined.
